<view class="doc-page legal-page">
  <view class="page-shell">
    <view class="panel rise-in legal-header">
      <view class="section-title">DocAI 用户协议</view>
      <view class="section-subtitle">更新时间：{{updatedAt}}</view>
      <view class="legal-note">
        请在注册和使用前仔细阅读本协议；如你不同意协议任一条款，请停止登录、注册或继续使用本小程序。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="panel rise-in legal-section" wx:for="{{sections}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="legal-section-title">{{item.title}}</view>
      <block wx:if="{{item.paragraphs}}">
        <view
          class="legal-paragraph"
          wx:for="{{item.paragraphs}}"
          wx:for-item="paragraph"
          wx:key="*this"
        >
          {{paragraph}}
        </view>
      </block>
      <block wx:if="{{item.bullets}}">
        <view
          class="legal-bullet"
          wx:for="{{item.bullets}}"
          wx:for-item="bullet"
          wx:key="*this"
        >
          {{bullet}}
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>

    <view class="panel rise-in">
      <view class="section-title">相关入口</view>
      <view class="section-subtitle">你可以继续查看隐私政策，或通过账号与安全页直接注销当前账号。</view>
      <view class="legal-actions">
        <button class="ghost-btn inline-btn legal-action-btn" bindtap="openPrivacyPolicy">查看隐私政策</button>
        <button class="solid-btn inline-btn legal-action-btn" bindtap="openAccountSecurity">账号与安全</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
